{"tid":756294,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普: 中國「惡毒」的舉動，最終一定會失敗","createTime":"2018-07-26T02:31:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-29T05:17:31.000Z","uid":62257,"like":53,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"628f4f2015e52a650403713c1998b69723585b13","tid":756294,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T02:31:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://ec.ltn.com.tw/m/article/breakingnews/2499533\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Fm%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2499533&d=TbmCC7jMkKUGLVsP2qrxg8n%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=d01a5b38\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Fm%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F2499533&h=b8e041cc\" target=\"_blank\">http://ec.ltn.com.tw/m/article/breakingnews/2499533</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/26/103112_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F26%2F103112_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=11bac755&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美中貿易戰日前再度升級，美國總統川普稱已準備對中國價值5050億美元商品加徵關稅。川普今發佈推文指出，美國有「軟弱的政客」希望停止貿易談判。川普表示，「每當我看到有軟弱的政客要求停止貿易談判，或撤銷對抗貿易不公的關稅時，我就想，他們還能想到什麼呢？ 我們應該繼續讓我們的農民和國家被剝削嗎？」，川普並稱，美國去年在國際貿易上損失817億美元（約新台幣2.4兆元），而美國「不會放下強硬的態度」。<br />\n川普也批評，要求停止貿易談判或撤銷關稅的行為是在「扯後腿」，只會讓協商拖得更長，而若美國團結起來，將會談成更好的交易。川普表示，「談判會非常成功，大家冷靜，結果會讓一切都值得」。<br />\n川普指出，中國在貿易戰中針對的目標，是「美國的農民」、「中國人知道我（川普）喜歡並且尊重美國農民」，也認為中國藉打擊美國農民，「試圖讓我放過中國，讓他們繼續佔美國便宜」，但中國「惡毒」的舉動，最終一定會失敗。<br />\n川普認為，不應該再容忍中國，「中國去年從我們身上賺走5170億美元（約新台幣15兆元）。我們過去一直忍受他們，但我們現在忍不下去了」。<br />\n為打擊川普票倉，美國農民一直是他國報復關稅的首要目標，美國則堅持不撤關稅，美農業部在週二宣布，將啟動共120億美元（約新台幣3678億元）的農民補助計劃。"},{"pid":"88365e4a8ac5121094bf29a110a5ef856cf3f440","tid":756294,"uid":52230,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T02:35:52.000Z","msg":"厲害了我的侵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9df6f3c67e202f002b8f3354fee30473bde1c6b1","tid":756294,"uid":113626,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T02:36:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/26/103626_82bcde3f8c7b449067ac1db4138e38cc.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F26%2F103626_82bcde3f8c7b449067ac1db4138e38cc.gif&h=5ecb1a9b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0b51d589d3d04f18db8a2af1a01c4c4c0d40da49","tid":756294,"uid":196719,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T02:39:21.000Z","msg":"中國或成最大贏家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad3e35e78f898122b50d2290a3913721a541145a","tid":756294,"uid":57376,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T03:07:30.000Z","msg":"「每當我看到有軟弱的政客要求停止貿易談判，或撤銷對抗貿易不公的關稅時，我就想，他們還能想到什麼呢？ 我們應該繼續讓我們的農民和國家被剝削嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n軟乜鬼弱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n擺明班人啲家族生意同贏國有關係啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c70359e7aa9a85c090e4a97917ce39f0064a1492","tid":756294,"uid":163350,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T03:10:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5ffc00c1b77f1f3b1a000eb04b13e81ce5f70d59","tid":756294,"uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ad3e35e78f898122b50d2290a3913721a541145a","tid":756294,"uid":57376,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T03:07:30.000Z","msg":"「每當我看到有軟弱的政客要求停止貿易談判，或撤銷對抗貿易不公的關稅時，我就想，他們還能想到什麼呢？ 我們應該繼續讓我們的農民和國家被剝削嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n軟乜鬼弱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n擺明班人啲家族生意同贏國有關係啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-26T03:15:10.000Z","msg":"錯晒啦，我識得大把呢啲美國